{"type":"message","id":"fda660da","parentId":"bd57040a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:21.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to use the quantitative system's already configured search skills and sources. Let me check what skills are available for stock/quantitative analysis. Looking at the available skills, I see:\n\n- akshare-stock: A股量化数据分析工具，基于AkShare库获取A股行情、财务数据、板块信息等\n- stock-watcher: Manage and monitor a personal stock watchlist\n- stock-market-pro: Yahoo Finance powered stock analysis\n- a-share-fusion-report: Generate a unified A-share report\n- news-market: 全球股市早间要闻生成技能\n\nLet me check the BOOTSTRAP.md - wait, the user said \"我量化系统已经配置好的搜索skill和来源\" - they have a quantitative system already configured with search skills and sources. \n\nIt looks like this workspace already has these skills installed, so I should focus on using the most relevant ones for their needs - probably akshare-stock for A-share data and stock-watcher for monitoring their portfolio.","thinkingSignature":"09be987acb33f994d1e8beef633203f5bc443f38414722c0a274634772d68137"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n好的，我来了解一下你已配置的量化系统情况。\n\n让我先看看 workspace 里有哪些相关的技能和配置：\n</final>\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_52i6t2921wx6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/skills/ 2>/dev/null && ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-downloader/ 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_52i6t2921wx6_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/akshare-stock/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":21713,"totalTokens":22136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774086851944}}
