ling  staff  1952 Mar 21 17:54 ..\ndrwx------   5 ling  staff   160 Mar  8 17:50 a-share-fusion-report\ndrwx------   3 ling  staff    96 Mar  5 11:01 agent-reach\ndrwx------   6 ling  staff   192 Mar  8 17:28 akshare-stock\ndrwx------  14 ling  staff   448 Mar  8 17:00 capability-evolver\ndrwx------@  6 ling  staff   192 Mar  6 22:54 deep-research-pro-1.0.2\ndrwx------   3 ling  staff    96 Mar  6 17:02 memory-profile\ndrwxr-xr-x  10 ling  staff   320 Mar  6 17:06 multi-search-engine\ndrwx------   5 ling  staff   160 Mar 14 08:56 news-market\ndrwx------   6 ling  staff   192 Mar 14 17:58 openclaw-workspace\ndrwx------@  4 ling  staff   128 Mar  6 22:53 slack-1.0.0\ndrwx------@  5 ling  staff   160 Mar  6 22:53 stock-market-pro-1.2.12\ndrwx------   7 ling  staff   224 Mar  8 17:28 stock-watcher\ndrwx------   8 ling  staff   256 Mar 18 00:53 xiaohongshu-skill\ndrwx------   7 ling  staff   224 Mar  9 17:17 xiaohongshutools\ntotal 64\ndrwx------  11 ling  staff   352 Mar 21 17:54 .\ndrwx------  61 ling  staff  1952 Mar 21 17:54 ..\ndrwx------   9 ling  staff   288 Mar 21 17:54 .git\ndrwx------   3 ling  staff    96 Mar 21 17:54 .openclaw\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff  7874 Mar 21 17:54 AGENTS.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff  1470 Mar 21 17:54 BOOTSTRAP.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff   168 Mar 21 17:54 HEARTBEAT.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff   636 Mar 21 17:54 IDENTITY.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff  1673 Mar 21 17:54 SOUL.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff   860 Mar 21 17:54 TOOLS.md\n-rw-------   1 ling  staff   477 Mar 21 17:54 USER.md","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-downloader"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774086861242}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd403e4f","parentId":"1b3a0883","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:21.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_52i6t2921wx6_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: akshare-stock\ndescription: A股量化数据分析工具，基于AkShare库获取A股行情、财务数据、板块信息等。用于回答关于A股股票查询、行情数据、财务分析、选股等问题。\n---\n\n# A股量化 - AkShare 数据接口\n\n## 快速开始\n\n安装依赖：\n```bash\npip install akshare\n```\n\n## 支持的功能\n\n### 1. 实时行情查询\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 个股实时行情\nstock_zh_a_spot_em()\nstock_zh_a_spot_em(symbol=\"北证A股\")\n```\n\n### 2. 历史K线数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 日K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"daily\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 周K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"weekly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 月K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"monthly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n```\n\n### 3. 财务数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 财务报表\nstock_financial_abstract_ths(symbol=\"000001\", indicator=\"按报告期\")\n\n# 主要财务指标\nstock_financial_analysis_indicator(symbol=\"000001\")\n```\n\n### 4. 板块/行业分析\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 行业板块行情\nstock_board_industry_name_em()\n\n# 概念板块行情\nstock_board_concept_name_em()\n\n# 板块内个股\nstock_board_industry_cons_em(symbol=\"半导体\")\n```\n\n### 5. 资金流向\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 个股资金流向\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\")\n\n# 大单净流入\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\", symbol=\"大单净流入\")\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"---\nname: akshare-stock\ndescription: A股量化数据分析工具，基于AkShare库获取A股行情、财务数据、板块信息等。用于回答关于A股股票查询、行情数据、财务分析、选股等问题。\n---\n\n# A股量化 - AkShare 数据接口\n\n## 快速开始\n\n安装依赖：\n```bash\npip install akshare\n```\n\n## 支持的功能\n\n### 1. 实时行情查询\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 个股实时行情\nstock_zh_a_spot_em()\nstock_zh_a_spot_em(symbol=\"北证A股\")\n```\n\n### 2. 历史K线数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 日K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"daily\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 周K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"weekly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n# 月K线\nstock_zh_a_hist(symbol=\"000001\", period=\"monthly\", start_date=\"20240101\", end_date=\"20241231\", adjust=\"qfq\")\n```\n\n### 3. 财务数据\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 财务报表\nstock_financial_abstract_ths(symbol=\"000001\", indicator=\"按报告期\")\n\n# 主要财务指标\nstock_financial_analysis_indicator(symbol=\"000001\")\n```\n\n### 4. 板块/行业分析\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 行业板块行情\nstock_board_industry_name_em()\n\n# 概念板块行情\nstock_board_concept_name_em()\n\n# 板块内个股\nstock_board_industry_cons_em(symbol=\"半导体\")\n```\n\n### 5. 资金流向\n\n```python\nimport akshare as ak\n\n# 个股资金流向\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\")\n\n# 大单净流入\nstock_individual_fund_flow(stock=\"000001\", market=\"sh\", symbol=\"大单净流入\")\n```","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-downloader"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774086861245}}
{"type":"message","id":"05302486","parentId":"dd403e4f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:26.797Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can see the quantitative skills are installed. Let me also check stock-watcher and the search engine skills to understand what's available.","thinkingSignature":"a99ce134fd487c7d7918f59849964cdad562893a593b0973f1bac95528a5288e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nlv2856fnpfr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/stock-watcher/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nlv2856fnpfr_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1616,"output":113,"cacheRead":21647,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23376,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774086861248}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8c0a3ec","parentId":"05302486","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:26.833Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nlv2856fnpfr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: stock-watcher\ndescription: Manage and monitor a personal stock watchlist with support for adding, removing, listing stocks, and summarizing their recent performance using data from 10jqka.com.cn. Use when the user wants to track specific stocks, get performance summaries, or manage their watchlist.\n---\n\n# Stock Watcher Skill\n\nThis skill provides comprehensive stock watchlist management capabilities, allowing users to track their favorite stocks and get performance summaries using real-time data from 同花顺 (10jqka.com.cn).\n\n## 自选股行情查看\n\n当你要求查看自选股行情时，系统会直接显示以下信息：\n- 每只股票的代码和名称\n- 近期表现指标（涨跌幅等关键数据）\n- 详细信息链接（可点击查看）\n\n无需额外命令，直接为你呈现简洁明了的行情概览。\n\n## 管理自选股\n\n### 添加股票\n使用股票代码（6位数字）添加到自选股：\n- 例如：添加 600053 九鼎投资\n\n### 删除股票  \n通过股票代码删除自选股：\n- 例如：删除 600053\n\n### 查看自选股列表\n显示当前所有自选股的完整列表\n\n### 清空自选股列表\n完全清空所有自选股\n\n## 数据来源\n\n主要使用**同花顺 (10jqka.com.cn)** 作为数据源：\n- **股票页面**: `https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{stock_code}/`\n- 支持沪深A股及科创板市场\n- 提供实时行情、技术分析和资金流向数据\n\n## 自选股管理\n\n### 文件格式\n自选股存储在 `~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`：\n```\n600053|九鼎投资\n600018|上港集团\n688785|恒运昌\n```\n\n### 支持操作\n1. **添加股票**: 验证股票代码格式并添加到自选股\n2. **删除股票**: 按股票代码精确匹配删除\n3. **查看列表**: 显示当前自选股\n4. **清空列表**: 完全清空自选股\n5. **行情总结**: 获取所有股票的最新数据并提供简洁摘要\n\n## 行情摘要特点\n\n- 直接显示关键行情指标，无冗余信息\n- 提供股票详情链接便于深入查看\n- 自动处理网络错误和数据异常\n- 合理控制请求频率（每秒1次）\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- **股票代码格式**: 使用6位数字代码（如 `600053`）\n- **数据延迟**: 行情可能有1-3分钟延迟\n- **网络依赖**: 需要网络连接获取实时数据\n- **市场范围**: 主要支持A股市场（沪市/深市/科创板）\n\n## 安装与卸载\n\n### 安装\n运行 `scripts/install.sh` 脚本自动创建必要的目录结构。\n\n### 卸载  \n运行 `scripts/uninstall.sh` 脚本完全移除所有相关文件。\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n所有脚本都使用统一的配置文件 `config.py` 来管理存储路径，确保路径一致性：\n- `add_stock.py` - 添加股票到自选股\n- `remove_stock.py` - 从自选股删除股票\n- `list_stocks.py` - 列出所有自选股\n- `clear_watchlist.py` - 清空自选股列表\n- `summarize_performance.py` - 获取股票行情摘要"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"---\nname: stock-watcher\ndescription: Manage and monitor a personal stock watchlist with support for adding, removing, listing stocks, and summarizing their recent performance using data from 10jqka.com.cn. Use when the user wants to track specific stocks, get performance summaries, or manage their watchlist.\n---\n\n# Stock Watcher Skill\n\nThis skill provides comprehensive stock watchlist management capabilities, allowing users to track their favorite stocks and get performance summaries using real-time data from 同花顺 (10jqka.com.cn).\n\n## 自选股行情查看\n\n当你要求查看自选股行情时，系统会直接显示以下信息：\n- 每只股票的代码和名称\n- 近期表现指标（涨跌幅等关键数据）\n- 详细信息链接（可点击查看）\n\n无需额外命令，直接为你呈现简洁明了的行情概览。\n\n## 管理自选股\n\n### 添加股票\n使用股票代码（6位数字）添加到自选股：\n- 例如：添加 600053 九鼎投资\n\n### 删除股票  \n通过股票代码删除自选股：\n- 例如：删除 600053\n\n### 查看自选股列表\n显示当前所有自选股的完整列表\n\n### 清空自选股列表\n完全清空所有自选股\n\n## 数据来源\n\n主要使用**同花顺 (10jqka.com.cn)** 作为数据源：\n- **股票页面**: `https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{stock_code}/`\n- 支持沪深A股及科创板市场\n- 提供实时行情、技术分析和资金流向数据\n\n## 自选股管理\n\n### 文件格式\n自选股存储在 `~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt`：\n```\n600053|九鼎投资\n600018|上港集团\n688785|恒运昌\n```\n\n### 支持操作\n1. **添加股票**: 验证股票代码格式并添加到自选股\n2. **删除股票**: 按股票代码精确匹配删除\n3. **查看列表**: 显示当前自选股\n4. **清空列表**: 完全清空自选股\n5. **行情总结**: 获取所有股票的最新数据并提供简洁摘要\n\n## 行情摘要特点\n\n- 直接显示关键行情指标，无冗余信息\n- 提供股票详情链接便于深入查看\n- 自动处理网络错误和数据异常\n- 合理控制请求频率（每秒1次）\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- **股票代码格式**: 使用6位数字代码（如 `600053`）\n- **数据延迟**: 行情可能有1-3分钟延迟\n- **网络依赖**: 需要网络连接获取实时数据\n- **市场范围**: 主要支持A股市场（沪市/深市/科创板）\n\n## 安装与卸载\n\n### 安装\n运行 `scripts/install.sh` 脚本自动创建必要的目录结构。\n\n### 卸载  \n运行 `scripts/uninstall.sh` 脚本完全移除所有相关文件。\n\n## 脚本说明\n\n所有脚本都使用统一的配置文件 `config.py` 来管理存储路径，确保路径一致性：\n- `add_stock.py` - 添加股票到自选股\n- `remove_stock.py` - 从自选股删除股票\n- `list_stocks.py` - 列出所有自选股\n- `clear_watchlist.py` - 清空自选股列表\n- `summarize_performance.py` - 获取股票行情摘要","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-downloader"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774086866830}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bf2ad96","parentId":"e8c0a3ec","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:26.836Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nlv2856fnpfr_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16,"aggregated":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace-downloader"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774086866833}}
{"type":"message","id":"c66b743c","parentId":"8bf2ad96","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:54:39.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good understanding of the available skills. Let me summarize what's configured:\n\n1. **akshare-stock** - A股量化数据（行情、财务、板块、资金流向）\n2. **stock-watcher** - 自选股管理（同花顺数据）\n3. **multi-search-engine** - 17个搜索引擎（百度、必应、谷歌、搜狗等）\n4. **news-market** - 全球股市早间要闻\n5. **a-share-fusion-report** - A股综合报告\n6. **stock-market-pro** - Yahoo Finance美股分析\n\n\n7. **deep-research-pro** - 深度研究\n8. **firecrawl** - 网页抓取\n\nI've got a solid toolkit ready to work with. I should let the user know what I've found and ask what they'd like to focus on.","thinkingSignature":"226cbaa2fd763693f7f51585da33496678bea4276d11e5437bc5d678261bf205"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n你的量化系统已经配置了以下技能/数据源：\n\n## 📊 A股数据\n- **akshare-stock** — 实时行情、历史K线、财务数据、板块、资金流向\n- **stock-watcher** — 自选股管理（基于同花顺）\n- **a-share-fusion-report** — 综合报告生成\n\n## 🔍 搜索工具\n- **multi-search-engine** — 17个搜索引擎（百度、必应、谷歌、搜狗、微信搜索、头条搜索、雪球、Yahoo、Bing等）\n- **deep-research-pro** — 深度研究agent\n\n## 📰 资讯\n- **news-market** — 全球股市早间要闻\n\n## 美股\n- **stock-market-pro** — Yahoo Finance（美股行情/技术指标/图表）\n\n---\n\n你想用这些工具做什么？比如：\n- 查某只A股的实时行情/财务数据\n- 搜索某个投资主题或资讯\n- 管理/查看自选股\n- 生成早间市场要闻\n- 其他量化分析任务\n\n直接告诉我需求就行。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3064,"output":406,"cacheRead":21647,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774086866836}}
